Package ChatSocketMulti.src.stream

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClientThread
    The Class ClientThread is a thread linked to a specific client where all the request sending by this client are treated.
    EchoClient
    The Class EchoClient is a class that create the interface for the client side of the Chat application.
    EchoServerMultiThreaded
    The Class EchoServerMultiThreaded is the class that initiate the thread of each client when one of them try to connect to the server.
    MessageClientThread
    The Class MessageClientThread is a thread launch in the client side to treat the request sending by the server and update the UI.
    Request
    The Class Request is a class that characterize a request send by a server to a client or send by a client to a server through a stream (Serializable).
